items.title: 'We need solutions': Palestinians in West Bank fear recognition is not enough
items.description: Many are concerned Israel may attempt to annex the occupied territory in response to several countries recognising Palestinian statehood.

items.title: British-Egyptian activist reunited with family after release from prison
